will there every be off camera he was the same kind of lovable 
fun mischievous guy you saw on television 
i hope never to be a big really big star cullen told the 
new york times in 1958 i may never be one in any case but ive 
seen too many big names burn themselves out on television 
cullen is survived by his wife ann 
