frawley a toxicologist at hercules corporate office in 
wilmington del to two officials at the jacksonville plant 
summarized a telephone call he received from earl farnham of dow 
dow was concerned about an acnegen or dioxin causing 
chloracne in workers at its 245t plant in midland mich 
they are aware that their competitors are marketing 245t 
which contains alarming amounts of acnegen and if the government 
learns of this the whole industry will suffer they are 
